                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "three times per day",
                    "effect": "You cast one of the following spells at the lowest level possible (unless otherwise specified):  *crushing despair* (one target within 30 feet only),  *fear* (3rd),  *paranoia* , or  *phantasmal killer* . You are exposed to the Empty Death each time you use this ability.",
